Package: iowagov
Title: State of Iowa Open Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Iowa Socrata Open Data portal (data.iowa.gov).
    Provides discovery, search, and data access for liquor sales, revenue,
    road conditions, unemployment, and 426+ state datasets.
